						<summary>

						<p>On the doorway of the Śiva temple called the Nāyakurāliguḍi in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Pramādi, Mārgaśira śu. 13, Sunday.</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of the <hi rend="italic">mukha-maṇḍapa</hi> of the temple of Chenna-Mallikhārjuna by Kākāṇḍi Mādaya for the merit of his father Mallaya. In characters of the 15th century A.D.</p>						

